""" Line number settings
set number
set relativenumber


""" Disabling arrow keys in insert mode 
nnoremap <UP> <NOP>
nnoremap <DOWN> <NOP>
nnoremap <RIGHT> <NOP>
nnoremap <LEFT> <NOP>

""" Copy & Paste to System Clipboards
set clipboard=unnamedplus

""" map escape to jk
inoremap jk <ESC>

""" settings for search
set hlsearch
set incsearch
